text:
Computer Scientist, Buisness Analylist, Data Scientist.

isaac@applesdofall.org | My wikipedia page



Bachelor of Science in Computer Science (Winter 2025 Rexburg, ID) Brigham Young University-Idaho • GPA: 3.91 • Computer Science Society • Minor in Business Analytics and DataScience • Brigham Young University Idaho Scholarship



Cashier (May 2019 – Jun. 2021 Burlington,NC) Chick-fil-A
• Greeted customers at the counter to fulfill orders and answer questions • Distributed to customer satisfaction with an average of 20 orders given per hour • Built connections with customers, resulting in an 80% satisfaction rate at that franchise • Handled cash transactions and point-of-sale operations
Skilled Labor June. 2021-Sep. 2021 Elite Garage High Point, NC
• Worked independently to meet productivity and quality expectations • Distributed materials and tools from storage facilities to worksite • Followed instructions and safety protocols to prevent accidents and injuries
Tutor – Team Lead Feb. 2024 – Present Study Buddies BYUI Rexburg, ID
• Created study plans and strategies for students success • Approved time submissions • Did individual interviews, presentations, and corrective actions • Participated in an Arbinger Program where we read Dangerous Love and Outward Mindset



Full-Time Volunteer Representative Sep. 2021 – Aug. 2023 The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints Colombia, Medellin
• Lived and worked with a variety of people from different backgrounds • Planned meetings, took care of finances, and sent in weekly reports • Helped support local leaders in communities, spoke publicly frequently, and helped plan activities



• Eagle Scout • Fluent in Spanish • Proficient in Python, HTML, CSS, and SQL • Now learning Linux, Java and C#
